<section class="sec reveal" id="qb-speak-form">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Discovery brief</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Tell us your QuickBooks situation.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">A Certified ProAdvisor replies within one business day with discovery-call slots. The brief is QuickBooks-focused &mdash; we use it to route you to the right ProAdvisor specialization (Desktop migration, payroll, multi-state setup, and so on). It is for the accounting work inside your books; if it&rsquo;s really an Intuit account or billing matter, we&rsquo;ll say so and point you to Intuit rather than book a call that can&rsquo;t help you.</p>

